otional and personal task as writing a fan letter.\", \"from\": 775, \"to\": 910, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 837, \"end\": 839, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.297431367532762e-14, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 790}, {\"ngram\": \"the ad\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 798}, {\"ngram\": \"backlash\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 812}, {\"ngram\": \"such an emotional and personal task\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 885}, {\"ngram\": \"a fan letter\", \"from\": 897, \"to\": 909}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Several called the message \\\"tone deaf\\\" and accused it of promoting laziness to create a letter devoid of meaning.\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 1024, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Several\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 918}, {\"ngram\": \"the message \\\"tone deaf\", \"from\": 926, \"to\": 948}, {\"ngram\": \"laziness\", \"from\": 978, \"to\": 986}, {\"ngram\": \"a letter\", \"from\": 997, \"to\": 1005}, {\"ngram\": \"meaning\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1023}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Having a child use Gemini to write a one-time letter, that is supposed to be thoughtful, where spelling and grammar mistakes would have surely been forgiven, is just plain dumb.\", \"from\": 1026, \"to\": 1204, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1046, \"end\": 1052, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gemini_Awards\", \"score\": 0.9931073939191706, \"rank\": 0.0069404438263037565, \"text\": \"Gemini\", \"types\": [\"Q618779\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gemini_Awards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gemini_Awards\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a child\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1041}, {\"ngram\": \"a one-time letter\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1079}, {\"ngram\": \"spelling\", \"from\": 1122, \"to\": 1130}, {\"ngram\": \"grammar mistakes\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1151}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I find myself judging the dad hard lol,\\\" one user wrote on the subreddit r/CommercialsIHate.\", \"from\": 1205, \"to\": 1297, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the dad\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1234}, {\"ngram\": \"one user\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1254}, {\"ngram\": \"the subreddit\", \"from\": 1264, \"to\": 1277}, {\"ngram\": \"r/CommercialsIHate\", \"from\": 1278, \"to\": 1296}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Others online said the advertisement, like others promoting Gemini, signalled that tech companies want people to think less and off-load creative thinking or social interactions to machines.\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1489, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Others\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1305}, {\"ngram\": \"the advertisement\", \"from\": 1318, \"to\": 1335}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 1342, \"to\": 1348}, {\"ngram\": \"Gemini\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1365}, {\"ngram\": \"tech companies\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1396}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1402, \"to\": 1408}, {\"ngram\": \"less and off-load creative thinking\", \"from\": 1418, \"to\": 1453}, {\"ngram\": \"social interactions\", \"from\": 1457, \"to\": 1476}, {\"ngram\": \"machines\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1488}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One such example criticised on Reddit included a Gemini commercial from May that, among other examples, showed a girl asking the chatbot what to say to her friends while they were sitting in front of her.\", \"from\": 1490, \"to\": 1694, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1521, \"end\": 1527, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reddit\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Reddit\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reddit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reddit\"}, {\"begin\": 1539, \"end\": 1545, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gemini_Awards\", \"score\": 0.9931073939