 \"The father\", \"from\": 1828, \"to\": 1838}, {\"ngram\": \"the video\", \"from\": 1842, \"to\": 1851}, {\"ngram\": \"his daughter\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1883}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead of guiding her to use her own words and communicate authentically, he is teaching her to rely on AI for this critical human skill,\\\" Palmer wrote.\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 2066, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2018, \"end\": 2020, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.297431367532762e-14, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her own words\", \"from\": 1943, \"to\": 1956}, {\"ngram\": \"this critical human skill\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2050}, {\"ngram\": \"Palmer\", \"from\": 2053, \"to\": 2059}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In response to a request for comment, a Google spokesperson said the ad was meant to show how Gemini can provide a starting point or draft to help with the writing process.\", \"from\": 2068, \"to\": 2240, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2108, \"end\": 2114, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.338298194017821e-13, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}, {\"begin\": 2162, \"end\": 2168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gemini_Awards\", \"score\": 0.9931073939191706, \"rank\": 0.0069404438263037565, \"text\": \"Gemini\", \"types\": [\"Q618779\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gemini_Awards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gemini_Awards\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"response\", \"from\": 2071, \"to\": 2079}, {\"ngram\": \"a request\", \"from\": 2083, \"to\": 2092}, {\"ngram\": \"comment\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2104}, {\"ngram\": \"the ad\", \"from\": 2133, \"to\": 2139}, {\"ngram\": \"a starting point\", \"from\": 2181, \"to\": 2197}, {\"ngram\": \"the writing process\", \"from\": 2220, \"to\": 2239}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We believe that AI can be a great tool for enhancing human creativity, but can never replace it,\\\" the spokesperson said.\", \"from\": 2242, \"to\": 2363, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2259, \"end\": 2261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.297431367532762e-14, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a great tool\", \"from\": 2269, \"to\": 2281}, {\"ngram\": \"human creativity\", \"from\": 2296, \"to\": 2312}, {\"ngram\": \"the spokesperson\", \"from\": 2341, \"to\": 2357}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the online criticism, the \\\"Dear Sydney\\\" commercial is one of the better performing Olympic advertisements, according to data from ad testing firm System1, cited byBusiness Insider.\", \"from\": 2365, \"to\": 2553, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the online criticism\", \"from\": 2373, \"to\": 2393}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"Dear Sydney\\\" commercial\", \"from\": 2395, \"to\": 2423}, {\"ngram\": \"the better performing Olympic advertisements\", \"from\": 2434, \"to\": 2478}, {\"ngram\": \"data\", \"from\": 2493, \"to\": 2497}, {\"ngram\": \"ad testing firm System1\", \"from\": 2503, \"to\": 2526}, {\"ngram\": \"byBusiness Insider\", \"from\": 2534, \"to\": 2552}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The firm gave the ad a 4.4 out of 5.9 (a score it described as \\\"strong\\\") on its scale of how much the commercial could create long-term growth for the brand.\", \"from\": 2554, \"to\": 2711, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The firm\", \"from\": 2554, \"to\": 2562}, {\"ngram\": \"the ad\", \"from\": 2568, \"to\":